snippet.title: Fallout: Tale of Two Wastelands Trailer 4K
snippet.description:
After three and a half long years, it's time to return to the wasteland with TTW 3.2!

https://taleoftwowastelands.com/download_ttw

With a changelog over 30000 lines long (when all weapon mesh fixes are condensed to one line), and a brand new installer capable of automatically installing all the utilities you'll need to run TTW and re-encoding Fallout 3's audio files, 3.2 is worth the wait!

My Instagram
https://www.instagram.com/lucian_hector/

Credits

Roy Batty and the TTW Team
Bethesda
Obsidian
